body.text:
{
    "live_stream": true,
    "ad_insertion": false,
    "region":"us-west-2",
    "reconnect_time": 0,
    "event_length": 0,
    "live_sliding_window_duration": 600,
    "metadata_passthrough": true,
    "add_cdns":[
      {
        "label": "akamai",
        "prepend": "tenausalive-a.akamaihd.net",
        "protocol": "https"
      }
    ],
    "outputs": [
     {
       "label": "hls720",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 1280,
       "height": 720,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 2500,
       "h264_profile": "high",
       "audio_bitrate": 128,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
     {
       "label": "hls576",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 1024,
       "height": 576,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 1700,
       "h264_profile": "main",
       "audio_bitrate": 128,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
     {
       "label": "hls432",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 768,
       "height": 432,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 1200,
       "h264_profile": "main",
       "audio_bitrate": 96,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
     {
       "label": "hls360",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 640,
       "height": 360,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 800,
       "h264_profile": "main",
       "audio_bitrate": 64,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
     {
       "label": "hls288",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 512,
       "height": 288,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 400,
       "h264_profile": "baseline",
       "audio_bitrate": 64,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
     {
       "label": "hls144",
       "live_stream": true,
       "width": 256,
       "height": 144,
       "video_codec": "h264",
       "video_bitrate": 160,
       "h264_profile": "baseline",
       "audio_bitrate": 64,
       "segment_seconds": 6,
       "keyframe_interval": 50
     },
        {
            "label": "playlist_all",
            "filename": "playlist-all.m3u8",
            "type": "playlist",
            "streams": [{"source": "hls720"},{"source": "hls576"},{"source": "hls432"},{"source": "hls360"},{"source": "hls288"},{"source": "hls144"}]
        },
        {
            "label": "playlist_sd",
            "filename": "playlist-sd.m3u8",
            "type": "playlist",
            "streams": [{"source": "hls576"},{"source": "hls432"},{"source": "hls360"},{"source": "hls288"},{"source": "hls144"}]
        }
    ]
}

{
    "live_stream": true,
    "ad_insertion": false,
    "region":"us-west-2",
    "reconnect_time": 0,
    "event_length": 0,
    "live_sliding_window_duration":7200,
    "metadata_passthrough": true,
    "outputs": [
        {
            "label": "hlstransmux",
            "live_stream": true,
            "copy_video": true,
            "segment_seconds": 6
        },
        {
            "label": "hls540p",
            "live_stream": true,
            "width": 960,
            "height": 540,
            "video_codec": "h264",
            "h264_profile": "main",
            "video_bitrate": 1200,
            "segment_seconds": 6,
            "video_keyframe_interval_follow_source": true
        }
    ]
}
